{"type":"message","id":"27ec74e7","parentId":"c79098a7","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:43:55.931Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 14th, 2026 — 21:43 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-14 13:43 UTC"}],"timestamp":1776174235925}}
{"type":"message","id":"80b0195f","parentId":"27ec74e7","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:43:56.722Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"你好呀，我是国寿龙虾，您的 AI 小帮手～目前还在内测阶段，能帮您搞定资讯收集、数据分析和文档编写，还能把琐事自动化哦！现在有什么想让我帮忙的吗？🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"my-qwen-provider","model":"AIAPLLM-vision-nothink","usage":{"input":17066,"output":47,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17113,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776174235930,"responseId":"chatcmpl-fefb5b49-7699-47c6-9cf9-5270ccf594ed"}}
