{"type":"message","id":"c2bdcb2e","parentId":"7b521464","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:44:27.944Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_49d2ea64a1cb4e12a0f811dd","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"agent:main:main\": {\n    \"sessionId\": \"c4803ea6-54cc-4d56-a500-bc98653190ca\",\n    \"updatedAt\": 1776174266366,\n    \"systemSent\": true,\n    \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n    \"chatType\": \"direct\",\n    \"deliveryContext\": {\n      \"channel\": \"webchat\"\n    },\n    \"origin\": {\n      \"provider\": \"webchat\",\n      \"surface\": \"webchat\",\n      \"chatType\": \"direct\"\n    },\n    \"sessionFile\": \"/home/node/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/c4803ea6-54cc-4d56-a500-bc98653190ca.jsonl\",\n    \"compactionCount\": 0,\n    \"skillsSnapshot\": {\n      \"prompt\": \"\\n\\nThe following skills provide specialized instructions for specific tasks.\\nUse the read tool to load a skill's file when the task matches its description.\\nWhen a skill file references a relative path, resolve it against the skill directory (parent of SKILL.md / dirname of the path) and use that absolute path in tool commands.\\n\\n<available_skills>\\n  <skill>\\n    <name>humanizer</name>\\n    <description>Remove signs of AI-generated writing from text. Use when editing or reviewing\\ntext to make it sound more natural and human-written. Based on Wikipedia&apos;s\\ncomprehensive &quot;Signs of AI writing&quot; guide. Detects and fixes patterns including:\\ninflated symbolism, promotional language, superficial -ing analyses, vague\\nattributions, em dash overuse, rule of three, AI vocabulary words, negative\\nparallelisms, and excessive conjunctive phrases.</description>\\n    <location>/app/skills/humanizer/SKILL.md</location>\\n  </skill>\\n  <skill>\\n    <name>security-triage</name>\\n    <description>Triage GitHub security advisories for OpenClaw with high-confidence close/keep decisions, exact tag and commit verification, trust-model checks, optional hardening notes, and a final reply ready to post and copy to clipboard.</description>\\n    <location>/app/skills/security-triage/SKILL.md</location>\\n  </skill>\\n  <skill>\\n    <name>imap-smtp-email</name>\\n    <description>Read and send email via IMAP/SMTP. Check for new/unread messages, fetch content, search mailboxes, mark as read/unread, and send emails with attachments. Supports multiple accounts. Works with any IMAP/SMTP server including Gmail, Outlook, 163.com, vip.163.com, 126.com, vip.126.com, 188.com, and vip.188.com.</description>\\n    <location>~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/imap-smtp-email/SKILL.md</location>\\n  </skill>\\n</available_skills>\",\n      \"skills\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"humanizer\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"security-triage\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"imap-smtp-email\",\n          \"requiredEnv\": []\n        }\n      ],\n      \"resolvedSkills\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"humanizer\",\n          \"description\": \"Remove signs of AI-generated writing from text. Use when editing or reviewing\\ntext to make it sound more natural and human-written. Based on Wikipedia's\\ncomprehensive \\\"Signs of AI writing\\\" guide. Detects and fixes patterns including:\\ninflated symbolism, promotional language, superficial -ing analyses, vague\\nattributions, em dash overuse, rule of three, AI vocabulary words, negative\\nparallelisms, and excessive conjunctive phrases.\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/app/skills/humanizer/SKILL.md\",\n          \"baseDir\": \"/app/skills/humanizer\",\n          \"source\": \"openclaw-bundled\",\n          \"sourceInfo\": {\n            \"path\": \"/app/skills/humanizer/SKILL.md\",\n            \"source\": \"openclaw-bundled\",\n            \"scope\": \"project\",\n            \"origin\": \"top-level\",\n            \"baseDir\": \"/app/skills/humanizer\"\n          },\n          \"disableModelInvocation\": false\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"security-triage\",\n          \"description\": \"Triage GitHub security advisories for OpenClaw with high-confidence close/keep decisions, exact tag and commit verification, trust-model checks, optional hardening notes, and a final reply ready to post and copy to clipboard.\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/app/skills/security-triage/SKILL.md\",\n          \"baseDir\": \"/app/skills/security-triage\",\n          \"source\": \"openclaw-bundled\",\n          \"sourceInfo\": {\n            \"path\": \"/app/skills/security-triage/SKILL.md\",\n            \"source\": \"openclaw-bundled\",\n            \"scope\": \"project\",\n            \"origin\": \"top-level\",\n            \"baseDir\": \"/app/skills/security-triage\"\n          },\n          \"disableModelInvocation\": false\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"imap-smtp-email\",\n          \"description\": \"Read and send email via IMAP/SMTP. Check for new/unread messages, fetch content, search mailboxes, mark as read/unread, and send emails with attachments. Supports multiple accounts. Works with any IMAP/SMTP server including Gmail, Outlook, 163.com, vip.163.com, 126.com, vip.126.com, 188.com, and vip.188.com.\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace/skills/imap-smtp-email/SKILL.md\",\n          \"baseDir\": \"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace/skills/imap-smtp-email\",\n          \"source\": \"openclaw-workspace\",\n          \"sourceInfo\": {\n            \"path\": \"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace/skills/imap-smtp-email/SKILL.md\",\n            \"source\": \"openclaw-workspace\",\n            \"scope\": \"project\",\n            \"origin\": \"top-level\",\n            \"baseDir\": \"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace/skills/imap-smtp-email\"\n          },\n          \"disableModelInvocation\": false\n        }\n      ],\n      \"version\": 0\n    },\n    \"modelProvider\": \"my-qwen-provider\",\n    \"model\": \"AIAPLLM-vision-nothink\",\n    \"systemPromptReport\": {\n      \"source